A modern inventory management API supporting both SQL (PostgreSQL) and NoSQL (DynamoDB) backends, designed for serverless AWS deployments.

## Features

- âœ… FastAPI endpoints for product/order management
- ğŸ”„ Dual database support (PostgreSQL + DynamoDB)
- ğŸ³ Dockerized Lambda deployment
- ğŸ”’ VPC security with RDS integration
- ğŸ“ˆ Auto-scaling serverless architecture

## Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Gao-tech/order_inventory_fastapi.git
cd order_inventory_fastapi

# Local setup
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

# AWS deployment
sam build
sam deploy --guided --resolve-image-repos


API Examples

POST /products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "09561633",
  "name": "Table and chairs",
  "category": "Dining Furniture",
  "price": 1700.00
}

Configuration

DB_HOST=your-rds-endpoint
DB_NAME=inventory_db
AWS_REGION=eu-north-1
```
